    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited for whoever ends up with this beauty! It is in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and there isn't a single scratch or mark to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and has been my pride and joy. If you're looking for something that's basically brand new but with a much more personal touch, you\u2019ve found it! Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
